<p>The trivial answer is <a href="https://docs.wpilib.org/en/stable/docs/software/dashboards/smartdashboard/index.html" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">HERE’S</a> the <code>SmartDashboard</code> documentation but that is simple enough that maybe there is more than this to your question.</p>
